    "We conducted a thorough assessment of the accuracy and thoroughness of the responses from each LLM-Chatbot.",
    "The ndings from our research could offer important insights into the advantages and drawbacks of utilizing LLM-Chatbots for providing information on common adolescent health and development issues.",
    "Methods EthicsGiven that no patients were involved in our study, approval from an ethics committee was not required.",
    "Study designOur study was conducted in the Pediatric Health Care Department of Huaibei People's Hospital from October 22, 2023, to November 29, 2023.In a collaborative effort, pediatrician Ying Li and data science student Zichen Song carefully compiled 100 pertinent questions on adolescent growth and development.",
